{"tid":2113533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有政黨到政總請願　促設臨時失業援助金及再派一萬元","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T09:00:30.000Z","uid":32577,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3512eddd76bf6bf74678b711435d9c8dfd5993","tid":2113533,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"民主黨幾名成員到政府總部外請願，要求政府向受到疫情影響而停工兩星期的員工及企業，推出工資補貼計劃及設立臨時失業援助金，並促請當局再次向全港市民派發一萬元。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨又要求政府強制所有入境人士，接受強制檢疫，在出現疫情小型爆發的社區，作出停工停市安排，以便全面消毒，杜絕疫情擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識玩"},{"pid":"57d261a77ba221b3a9c51323bc1d39e01237bba2","tid":2113533,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1538540_1_L_20200718152946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1538540_1_L_20200718152946.jpg&h=5ee75662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2176c75648441292003f61dcb6e0af160cf647c3","tid":2113533,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538540-20200718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538540-20200718.htm&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=cc41b8db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538540-20200718.htm&h=e968bcd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538540-20200718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1c75e5655c3c3a06fa8114c424c4a398215b3d88","tid":2113533,"uid":11067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"無啲志氣 起碼都五萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f895b86d64390193adb0139ac4ac6c2181a7576","tid":2113533,"uid":24080,"like":2